When a player reaches level 20, he has several options.  If he
has successfully completed all the quests, he may apply for
wizardhood and become part of the coding team here at Darkwind.
If he has a quest or 2 left, he can continue adventuring, gaining
additional levels, until he finishes the quest at which point he can
apply for wizardhood.  If you have no desire to become a wizard but
enjoy playing, you can continue advancing your levels all the way
up to level 90.  For those who don't want to wiz but also want more out
of life, you can become a noble.  Nobles are discused in more detail
in chapter 14.
